c: 31
v: 29
t: Kya tum dekhte nahin ho ke Allah raat ko din mein pirota hua le aata hai aur din ko raat mein? Usne Suraj aur chand ko musakkhar (subjected) kar rakkha hai. Sab ek waqt e muqarrar tak chale jaa rahey hain. Aur (kya tum nahin jantey) ke jo kuch bhi tum karte ho Allah ussey ba-kharbar hai